Accounts and visitors are fetched via the Pendo Aggregation API (`POST /api/v1/aggregation`). The request body uses a pipeline structure:
```json
{
  "response": {"mimeType": "application/json"},
  "request": {
    "pipeline": [
      {"source": {"accounts": null}},
      {"limit": 100}
    ]
  }
}
```
